Rémy Martin is back with its customisable metal neck tag for the iconic XO bottle, which can be engraved with a personal message. This produces a unique decanter that will sit beautifully on display at home or be shared on a special occasion. It’s the perfect gift for the person who has it all. Rémy Martin XO is the signature of our Cellar Master who with his expertise blends up to 400 eaux-de-vie. His art of blending allows for the expression of the full aromatic complexity of this XO Cognac Fine Champagne, making this the perfect spirit to celebrate with. Watch the video | Rémy Martin XO personalised gift  Place your order on the Exceptional Spirits store before midnight on June 12 to receive the bottle nationwide in time for Father’s Day. Delivery is free for all orders made in the store. Rémy Martin will also be rolling out the red carpet at three stores in Johannesburg where the decanters will be engraved directly in-store, on the day. The engraving is done by in-house specialists, and takes as little as 5 minutes to do. Rémy Martin XO in-store engraving dates and times for Johannesburg: Note: The engraving is done on a well-fitted golden collar that clips onto the decanter. Personal messages can be applied, up to three lines. DM